title: 2 Bedroom Just for You!
posting_body: ['Take a Virtual Tour Today!', '<URL>', "Welcome to Sloan's Lake", 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 919 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Indulge in a relaxing refuge from the workday world by swimming, taking a dip in the Jacuzzi or even a peaceful stroll.', "Discover Sloan's Lake where natural beauty and contemporary design come together in a distinctive apartment community expressly planned for your living enjoyment.", "Sloan's Lake is located within minutes of everything exciting in Denver-fine dining, theaters, shopping and recreation.", 'A wealth of shopping possibilities abound...', "Belmar, Colorado Mills, Super Wal Mart, and JCR The recreational opportunities of Sloan's Lake and the Rocky Mountains are minutes away.", "Find the your key to happiness at Sloan's Lake.", 'Residents love us on Apartment Ratings!', '<URL>', 'Features:', 'Extra Storage, Porcelain Tubs, Stainless Steel Appliances*, Custom 2-Tone Paint*, Window Coverings, Ceiling Fans, Wheelchair Access*, Air Conditioner, Plush Berber Carpet*, Stone Wood-Burning Fireplaces, Kitchen Pantries*, Disposal, Skylights*, Handrails*, Patios/Balconies, Granite-Style Countertops*, Faux Wood Floors, Refrigerator, Vaulted Ceilings*, Cable Ready, Oak Cabinetry,  Washer/Dryer, Dishwasher, Brushed Nickel Fixtures*', '*in select units', 'Community Amenities:', 'On-Site Management, On-Site Maintenance, Bike Racks, Short Term Leases Available, Year-Round Spa, High Speed Internet, Package Receiving, Garage Rentals Available, Clubhouse, Covered Parking Available, Business Center, Sparkling Swimming Pool, Close to Public Transportation, Recycling, On-Site Laundry Facility, Barbecue Area with Grills', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'TOa0r1pw']
